    "The first paper discussed Advanced Persistent Threats (APT) detection-related challenges and unsolved issues using ML.",
    "Hackers target Internet of Things (IoT) systems for a variety of reasons, including disclosing, shifting, disabling, copying, or obtaining unauthorised access to or using an asset without authorization.",
